<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Premium Career Guide</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0b1220;
  --panel:#0e172a;
  --text:#e6e9ef;
  --muted:#9aa3b2;
  --accent:#7c9cff;
  --accent2:#22d3ee;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  color:var(--text);
  background:
    radial-gradient(900px 500px at 0% 0%, rgba(124,156,255,.25), transparent),
    radial-gradient(800px 400px at 100% 0%, rgba(34,211,238,.2), transparent),
    var(--bg);
}

header{
  text-align:center;
  padding:60px 16px 30px;
  animation:fadeDown .7s ease both;
}
header h1{
  margin:0 0 10px;
  font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
  font-size:2.6rem;
  letter-spacing:.5px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));
  -webkit-background-clip:text; color:transparent;
}
header p{margin:0;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px}

.container{max-width:960px;margin:auto;padding:20px}

.track{position:relative;padding-left:26px}
.track::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;left:10px;top:0;bottom:0;width:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(var(--accent), transparent);
}

.item{position:relative;margin:20px 0;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);animation:fadeUp .7s forwards}
.item:nth-child(1){animation-delay:.2s}
.item:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.4s}
.item:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.6s}
.item:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.8s}

.dot{
  position:absolute;left:4px;top:18px;width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));
  box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(34,211,238,.6);
}

.card{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  border-radius:16px;
  padding:20px;
  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  transition:.3s;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
}

.card:hover{
  transform:translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
  box-shadow:0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
  border-color:rgba(124,156,255,.5);
}

.card::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(120deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,.15), transparent);
  opacity:0;transform:translateX(-60%);
}
.card:hover::after{opacity:1;animation:shine .9s}

.title{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:10px}
.title h2{margin:0;font-size:1.2rem;color:#fff}
.badge{
  font-size:12px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));
  color:#000;font-weight:600;
}

.list{display:grid;gap:6px}
.list p{margin:0;font-size:14px}
.sub{color:var(--muted)}

.icon{
  position:absolute;right:15px;top:15px;font-size:18px;opacity:.6
}

@keyframes fadeUp{to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes fadeDown{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes shine{to{transform:translateX(60%);opacity:0}}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Career Guide</h1>
  <p>Simple, attractive & premium path after 10th & 12th</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
<div class="track">

<div class="item">
  <div class="dot"></div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">🎓</div>
    <div class="title">
      <h2>After 10th</h2>
      <span class="badge">Start</span>
    </div>
    <div class="list">
      <p>📘 Science → Doctor / Engineer</p>
      <p>📗 Commerce → Business / Accounts</p>
      <p>📕 Arts → Govt jobs / Teaching</p>
      <p class="sub">🛠 ITI / Diploma → Quick job + skill</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="item">
  <div class="dot"></div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">📚</div>
    <div class="title">
      <h2>After 12th</h2>
      <span class="badge">Choose</span>
    </div>
    <div class="list">
      <p>Science → Engineering / Medical</p>
      <p>Commerce → B.Com / CA / Business</p>
      <p>Arts → BA / Law / Govt exams</p>
      <p class="sub">💼 Direct jobs → Office / Sales / Govt</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="item">
  <div class="dot"></div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">💡</div>
    <div class="title">
      <h2>Smart Option</h2>
      <span class="badge">Best</span>
    </div>
    <div class="list">
      <p>✔ Study + Skill together</p>
      <p>💻 Computer skills</p>
      <p>🎨 Design</p>
      <p>🎬 Editing / 🌐 Online work</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="item">
  <div class="dot"></div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">🏆</div>
    <div class="title">
      <h2>Final Formula</h2>
      <span class="badge">Rule</span>
    </div>
    <div class="list">
      <p>👉 Interest + Skill + Hard Work = Success</p>
      <p>After 10th → Choose stream</p>
      <p>After 12th → Choose course/job</p>
      <p class="sub">Always → Learn skills</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
